可以停<br />\n既然中共自稱滿清正統承繼人<br />\n呢張債券自然本利點都要還<br />\n唔還既佢講乜差野要用南京條約去收番香港<br />\n而且美國政府係未同中共追還錢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wjpU2AG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwjpU2AG.jpg&h=45a46f02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">緊係侵侵啦！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/special2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/special3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"4725fff97e0f0242d918783c4f1d5503a5605417","tid":1571290,"uid":98431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T11:38:59.000Z","msg":"班狗改左策略 玩接放學<br />\n<br />\n老銅狗已全部縮返狗鐵個洞 小心去其他區咬人"},{"pid":"e90e89e59c387e6d8b829fd32519a345084fc6bf","tid":1571290,"uid":210612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T11:39:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">珍惜生命 遠離狗鐵</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"f313b0df61fd5b013117aefe1301bdd328a10093","tid":1571290,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T11:41:12.000Z","msg":"九龍灣一架豬籠車"},{"pid":"0c104dec2cdc1f2cbcf5eee448aed88fb0833491","tid":1571290,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T11:59:33.000Z","msg":"咪搭地鐵"},{"pid":"5573c209e17d1bce190980950e5829783c78f97d","tid":1571290,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T12:00:31.000Z","msg":"好"},{"pid":"57cfc15ed61aa500775170096889b64bc5dbfba1","tid":1571290,"uid":30990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T12:01:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6cb6eb3ae333ec74c06c18a7f39c5c13c4b00e97","tid":1571290,"uid":306469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T12:02:58.000Z","msg":"我巴士經過見到有狗車停左嚮馬路"},{"pid":"81cbaff4e0411d3bd8ec0bc96ad6bc037094d436","tid":1571290,"uid":20